1
00:01:09,820 --> 00:01:13,500
=Inherently Kind=

2
00:01:14,780 --> 00:01:17,700
=Episode 4=
(The Rise of a Female CEO)

3
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:23,840
Thank you.

4
00:01:24,319 --> 00:01:25,159
You saved me again.

5
00:01:25,760 --> 00:01:26,519
Just by chance.

6
00:01:27,519 --> 00:01:28,519
With your skills,

7
00:01:29,280 --> 00:01:30,120
you could have handled it alone.

8
00:01:32,040 --> 00:01:33,719
I did not expect I could
fight like that either.

9
00:01:35,120 --> 00:01:36,159
But still, thank you.

10
00:01:37,040 --> 00:01:38,000
Thank you for this sports car.

11
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:41,400
Your driving skills

12
00:01:42,040 --> 00:01:42,920
are also quite impressive.

13
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:13,360
Your car drives great.

14
00:02:16,879 --> 00:02:19,439
You're not at all what I heard.

15
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:20,360
Is that so?

16
00:02:22,599 --> 00:02:23,680
I don't really fit the image

17
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:25,520
of a rich heiress, do I?

18
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:27,520
No one has ever defined

19
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:29,199
what a wealthy heiress should be like.

20
00:02:30,479 --> 00:02:31,159
But

21
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:34,919
you are very much like
the person in my impression.

22
00:02:36,759 --> 00:02:39,240
Are we very close?

23
00:02:40,199 --> 00:02:40,919
We...

24
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:42,360
We were very intimate.

25
00:02:44,080 --> 00:02:44,800
Does that count?

26
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:50,120
You could not be my
ex-boyfriend, could you?

27
00:02:56,100 --> 00:02:59,020
(Southeast Asia Border)

28
00:02:59,719 --> 00:03:00,479
(Hey, lady.)

29
00:03:02,639 --> 00:03:04,319
(Let's have a drink.)

30
00:03:04,639 --> 00:03:05,719
(No more drinks...)

31
00:03:06,919 --> 00:03:07,879
(So annoying!)

32
00:03:12,599 --> 00:03:13,599
(Let go!)

33
00:03:19,479 --> 00:03:20,120
(Let go!)

34
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:21,439
(Let go!)

35
00:03:26,879 --> 00:03:28,000
(Are you Chinese?)

36
00:03:28,479 --> 00:03:29,120
(Help me!)

37
00:03:29,719 --> 00:03:30,520
(Take me away!)

38
00:03:40,080 --> 00:03:41,280
(You have been drugged.)

39
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:46,960
(You talk too much.)

40
00:03:47,120 --> 00:03:48,680
(Are you a man?)

41
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:11,520
A woman

42
00:04:12,919 --> 00:04:13,800
slept with me,

43
00:04:14,080 --> 00:04:15,199
and then just disappeared.

44
00:04:16,279 --> 00:04:17,560
And now she's faking amnesia.

45
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:24,800
Am I really that heartless?

46
00:04:25,879 --> 00:04:27,319
(She does not seem to be faking it.)

47
00:04:28,279 --> 00:04:29,439
(Could she really have amnesia?)

48
00:04:32,439 --> 00:04:33,759
Anyway, it's water under the bridge.

49
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:36,040
Forget it, then.

50
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:38,240
I am a businessman.

51
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:39,839
For me,

52
00:04:40,399 --> 00:04:41,519
profit is the most important thing.

53
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:45,040
Once you take over Gu Corporation,

54
00:04:46,160 --> 00:04:47,399
we can still work together.

55
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:53,199
Hello?

56
00:04:56,959 --> 00:04:57,439
Alright.

57
00:04:57,639 --> 00:04:59,079
I will be there on time tomorrow.

58
00:05:02,959 --> 00:05:05,519
They want me to attend
the shareholders' meeting tomorrow.

59
00:05:05,879 --> 00:05:07,000
I know nothing about it.

60
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:08,800
Do you need my help?

61
00:05:09,839 --> 00:05:10,480
How can you help?

62
00:05:15,900 --> 00:05:18,180
(Gu Corporation)

63
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:20,639
What is this?

64
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:22,439
This is what I've gathered.

65
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:24,279
Maybe it can help you.

66
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:30,000
Where did you get this?

67
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:33,560
I acquired ten percent
of Gu Corporation's shares.

68
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,040
So of course I do my homework.

69
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:37,160
But the information here

70
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:38,800
is quite extensive.

71
00:05:38,959 --> 00:05:40,800
You may need to find out
some issues yourself.

72
00:05:40,959 --> 00:05:41,600
No problem.

73
00:05:42,759 --> 00:05:43,399
Thank you.

74
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:44,560
You have helped me again.

75
00:05:58,879 --> 00:05:59,399
Give it a try.

76
00:06:01,079 --> 00:06:03,800
Meiyan's latest
miracle essence repair serum.

77
00:06:04,879 --> 00:06:06,160
You will be satisfied with the results.

78
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:08,519
Why me?

79
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:11,240
Because

80
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:13,000
you are greedy enough.

81
00:06:27,839 --> 00:06:29,040
Look who finally showed up!

82
00:06:31,079 --> 00:06:32,759
You've been gone all day.

83
00:06:33,759 --> 00:06:35,600
Were you out messing around?

84
00:06:35,759 --> 00:06:36,519
According to law,

85
00:06:36,839 --> 00:06:38,800
even married women are entitled
to their own freedom.

86
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:40,120
Stop right there!

87
00:06:41,480 --> 00:06:42,600
Go wash the dishes in the kitchen!

88
00:06:43,199 --> 00:06:43,759
Sorry.

89
00:06:43,879 --> 00:06:45,600
I have to attend Gu Corporation's
shareholders' meeting tomorrow.

90
00:06:45,759 --> 00:06:46,920
I need to rest early tonight.

91
00:06:47,439 --> 00:06:47,920
Good night.

92
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:48,720
Jinchen.

93
00:06:49,279 --> 00:06:50,639
Look at your wife.

94
00:06:51,079 --> 00:06:52,439
She has really become bold!

95
00:06:52,879 --> 00:06:54,600
She was out fooling around all day.

96
00:06:55,279 --> 00:06:58,319
I guess she'll probably
start staying out all night.

97
00:06:59,040 --> 00:06:59,519
Mom.

98
00:07:00,199 --> 00:07:01,639
Qingmei needs to attend
the shareholders' meeting.

99
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:02,839
She has been really tired lately.

100
00:07:03,399 --> 00:07:04,240
Please go easy on her.

101
00:07:19,639 --> 00:07:20,439
I'm sleeping here tonight.

102
00:07:23,920 --> 00:07:25,360
Suit yourself.

103
00:07:25,680 --> 00:07:26,160
By the way,

104
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:27,680
tomorrow's shareholders' meeting,

105
00:07:28,279 --> 00:07:29,160
I'll go with you.

106
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:31,120
Alright.

107
00:08:52,279 --> 00:08:52,960
(Who's there?)

108
00:08:54,720 --> 00:08:55,399
(Stop right there!)

109
00:08:59,799 --> 00:09:00,320
What...

110
00:09:00,559 --> 00:09:01,120
Gu Qingmei.

111
00:09:01,759 --> 00:09:02,639
What are you doing?

112
00:09:04,519 --> 00:09:05,080
I am sorry.

113
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:05,720
I... I...

114
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:07,639
I was too nervous. I had a dream.

115
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:08,200
I...

116
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,000
Fine.

117
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:14,480
Alright.

118
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:18,240
Maybe you are under too much pressure.

119
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:19,679
Get some good rest.

120
00:09:22,639 --> 00:09:23,200
Don't worry.

121
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:24,720
In tomorrow's meeting,

122
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:26,200
I will help you.

123
00:09:54,639 --> 00:09:55,720
What a joke!

124
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:57,519
A housewife

125
00:09:57,639 --> 00:09:58,840
managing a publicly listed company?

126
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:00,639
She probably can't even
read a financial statement.

127
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:03,279
Though she does not understand finance,

128
00:10:03,480 --> 00:10:05,000
her husband is Mr. He.

129
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:05,960
I believe

130
00:10:06,159 --> 00:10:08,440
Mr. He should manage
the company on her behalf.

131
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:10,200
If she becomes the chairman,

132
00:10:10,320 --> 00:10:11,360
I will pull out my shares immediately!

133
00:10:11,799 --> 00:10:12,279
Me too!

134
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:12,960
Me too!

135
00:10:13,039 --> 00:10:13,360
Me too!

136
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:14,639
Yes, we're all pulling out!

137
00:10:29,879 --> 00:10:31,000
I hear you want to pull out?

138
00:10:31,759 --> 00:10:32,320
No problem.

139
00:10:33,279 --> 00:10:34,360
But before that,

140
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:36,480
I have a few questions.

141
00:10:38,519 --> 00:10:39,279
(Capital Flow Chart)
Question one.

142
00:10:40,919 --> 00:10:42,840
This is the subsidiary
you're in charge of, Mr. Wang.

143
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:44,240
Logistics costs

144
00:10:44,399 --> 00:10:46,799
(Subsidiary Annual Revenue)
have increased by 200 percent.

145
00:10:48,759 --> 00:10:50,200
May I ask where this money went?

146
00:10:51,399 --> 00:10:52,200
Question two.

147
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:58,679
This is a PO of building materials.

148
00:10:59,080 --> 00:11:01,440
The unit price of building materials
is ten times higher than before.

149
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:04,000
The signature belongs to your nephew,
Mr. Wang.

150
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:06,039
Such misappropriation of company assets,

151
00:11:06,879 --> 00:11:07,720
were you aware of it?

152
00:11:10,159 --> 00:11:12,519
Even a housewife can see this clearly.

153
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:16,399
Would you like to explan

154
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:17,279
to the shareholders here?

155
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:24,200
Maybe the statements were wrong.

156
00:11:24,480 --> 00:11:25,600
I'll look into it carefully
when I get back.

157
00:11:27,639 --> 00:11:28,679
I also have questions

158
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:30,360
regarding several other shareholders.

159
00:11:31,039 --> 00:11:32,600
Do I need to ask you one by one?

160
00:11:33,279 --> 00:11:33,799
Mr. Liu?

161
00:11:34,720 --> 00:11:35,320
Mr. Zhang?

162
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:36,799
Mr. Tian?

163
00:11:37,120 --> 00:11:37,720
Madam Gu!

164
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:38,720
As for the other issues,

165
00:11:39,039 --> 00:11:40,279
we will settle them after the meeting.

166
00:11:40,879 --> 00:11:42,000
Today we are discussing

167
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:43,440
your appointment.

168
00:11:45,440 --> 00:11:46,120
Alright.

169
00:11:47,159 --> 00:11:49,200
Any other objections to my appointment?

170
00:11:55,519 --> 00:11:56,080
I agree.

171
00:11:57,159 --> 00:11:59,679
Madam Gu shall serve as the
Chairman of Gu Corporation.

172
00:12:05,159 --> 00:12:05,759
I agree too.

173
00:12:05,879 --> 00:12:06,399
Agree.

174
00:12:06,759 --> 00:12:07,519
I agree.

175
00:12:08,039 --> 00:12:09,000
Agree.

176
00:12:09,799 --> 00:12:10,480
Agree.

177
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:13,879
Good.

178
00:12:16,039 --> 00:12:17,039
Then

179
00:12:19,360 --> 00:12:20,120
meeting adjourned.

180
00:12:23,399 --> 00:12:24,159
I did not expect

181
00:12:24,320 --> 00:12:26,000
that the mysterious businessman

182
00:12:26,080 --> 00:12:26,799
who acquired ten percent shares

183
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:28,159
turns out to be you, Mr. Mu.

184
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:30,919
I did not expect either

185
00:12:31,919 --> 00:12:34,360
that you would attend the meeting
as a family member.

186
00:12:36,639 --> 00:12:37,639
My wife's matters

187
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:39,240
are naturally my matters.

188
00:12:49,120 --> 00:12:51,000
Thank you for helping me
secure the position of chairman.

189
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:06,840
Sometimes I am truly curious.

190
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:10,039
Who exactly are you?

191
00:13:13,679 --> 00:13:14,759
I'm also very confused.

192
00:13:16,559 --> 00:13:17,799
Every morning when I wake up,

193
00:13:17,960 --> 00:13:19,360
I have to check in the mirror.

194
00:13:20,159 --> 00:13:20,840
Mrs. He?

195
00:13:21,759 --> 00:13:22,759
Heir of Gu Corporation?

196
00:13:24,919 --> 00:13:25,519
I don't know.

197
00:13:26,399 --> 00:13:27,480
But I always feel these identities

198
00:13:27,519 --> 00:13:29,679
are like the wrong outfits

199
00:13:30,480 --> 00:13:31,759
that never quite feel right.

200
00:13:32,519 --> 00:13:33,399
No matter who you are,

201
00:13:35,399 --> 00:13:36,360
I will help you.

202
00:13:38,320 --> 00:13:39,519
Why do you want to help me?

203
00:13:40,159 --> 00:13:41,399
What exactly do you want?

204
00:13:42,320 --> 00:13:43,000
The truth.

205
00:13:44,519 --> 00:13:45,960
I only want the truth.

206
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:50,600
I might have said that too.

207
00:14:11,300 --> 00:14:16,060
♪Time stole the proof of our love♪

208
00:14:16,060 --> 00:14:20,900
♪Hidden in the moonlight,
lost in the clouds♪

209
00:14:20,900 --> 00:14:25,460
♪Tangled glances and love fall together♪

210
00:14:25,460 --> 00:14:30,380
♪Into a spiral of thoughts,
memories rewinding♪

211
00:14:30,380 --> 00:14:34,180
♪Feelings both strange and familiar♪

212
00:14:34,180 --> 00:14:38,980
♪I just know you're
where my heart belongs♪

213
00:14:38,980 --> 00:14:41,820
♪Can't remember when
this flutter started♪

214
00:14:41,820 --> 00:14:44,500
♪Or how it's supposed to end♪

215
00:14:44,860 --> 00:14:50,420
♪Goodbye to the world rushing in♪

216
00:14:50,820 --> 00:14:57,620
♪Let me hide in your eyes
and never leave♪

217
00:14:57,900 --> 00:15:02,580
♪Feel the rhythm of your heartbeat♪

218
00:15:02,740 --> 00:15:09,540
♪Every tomorrow seems worth the wait♪

219
00:15:09,860 --> 00:15:16,660
♪Let me fill the emptiness of a century♪

220
00:15:16,860 --> 00:15:21,340
♪As the wind brushes past your hem♪

221
00:15:21,340 --> 00:15:24,700
♪All my hidden feelings come undone♪

222
00:15:24,700 --> 00:15:31,620
♪Right as I confess my love♪
